---
title: Queso Fundido-Inspired Tacos with Chipotle Chorizo, Corn and Lime Crema
description: We're making taco night extra special by taking a cue from queso fundido! Monterey Jack cheese is melted on flour tortillas, which are topped with smoky chipotle chorizo and a fresh pepper and tomato pico de gallo. A dollop of lime crema brightens up every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-style-queso-fundido-7d2d0025.jpg
